Package social.wall

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FriendWallMenu
    The FriendWallMenu class interacts with the user on the Friends' Wall Page
    GiftAccepter
    The GiftAccepter class accepts a user's gifts
    TagManager
    The TagManager class retrieves and deletes tags from a thread
    WallCtrl
    The WallCtrl class facilitates the interaction between the database and the WallMenu or FriendWallMenu
    WallGetter
    The WallGetter class retrieves threads from a wall
    WallMenu
    The WallMenu class interacts with the user on the My Wall Page
    WallPoster
    The WallPoster class posts threads to a wall
    WallUtility
    The WallUtility class contains the utility functions for dealing with walls
